EACH MUST BE LESS THAN 9999999. 610.0 *** USER WARNING/FATAL MESSAGE 610 (IFP1D) THE VALUE FOLLOWING THE EQUAL SIGN ON THE ABOVE CARD IS ILLEGAL.
